OL,3,CDurrell on the hunt for a new CEO
OL,5,FDurrell Wildlife Conservation Trust is
OL,6,Fon the hunt for a new Chief Executive
OL,7,FOfficer.
OL,9,FThe trust has suffered a turbulent
OL,10,Fperiod, facing criticism over animal
OL,11,Fwelfare concerns and the treatment of
OL,12,Fstaff at Jersey Zoo.
OL,14,FRebecca Brewer, who was acting as the
OL,15,Fhead of the Trust has stepped down as
OL,16,Finterim CEO.
