OL,3,CDurrell on the hunt for a new CEO
OL,5,FResponding to allegations of a "toxic
OL,6,Fworkplace" and animal welfare concerns
OL,7,Fshe told ITV News: "This is an
OL,8,Fincredibly challenging time for
OL,9,Feveryone and it's had a great impact
OL,10,Fon everyone here at Durrell but
OL,11,Fespecially those who care so
OL,12,Fpassionately for our animals."
OL,14,FShe temporarily stepped up from her
OL,15,Frole as Finance Director to interim
OL,16,Fleader after Dr Lesley Dickie resigned
OL,17,Fin September 2023.
OL,19,FRebecca Brewer has not yet commented
OL,20,Fon her move away from the job.
