OL,3,CDurrell on the hunt for a new CEO
OL,5,FThe Trust hopes that a new CEO will
OL,6,Flead Durrell into an "exciting next
OL,7,Fchapter".
OL,9,FDurrell's Chair, Matthew Hatchwell
OL,10,Fsaid: "We look forward to hearing from
OL,11,Fcandidates who feel inspired to join
OL,12,Fus on our journey in creating a
OL,13,Fwilder, healthier, and more colourful
OL,14,Fworld for both people and wildlife."
OL,16,FAs well as recruiting a new CEO, the
OL,17,Ftrust is also looking to elect four
OL,18,Fnew trustees to its Board later this
OL,19,Fyear.
